{"tid":1868330,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Switch 、其周邊、健身環供貨受武漢肺炎影響","createTime":"2020-02-07T13:43:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T14:42:44.000Z","uid":79075,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e83fbdf49f172f2a911813ba58b20ca297eb7f36","tid":1868330,"uid":79075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T13:43:03.000Z","msg":"親愛的顧客<br />\n2020年2月6日<br />\n<br />\n任天堂（香港）有限公司<br />\n關於2019新型冠狀病毒(2019-nCoV)<br />\n對Nintendo Switch等之生產製造及運輸之影響<br />\n感謝各位對本公司的愛顧和支持。<br />\n<br />\n受現正出現的2019新型冠狀病毒(2019-nCoV)疫情影響，將對在中國工場生產的Nintendo Switch 主機及Joy-Con等周邊設備等之製造及運輸將造成無可避免的影響。此外，現在處於貨源短缺情況的Nintendo Switch《健身環大冒險》之運輸也會受到影響而延遲。 對顧客造成不便，本公司深感抱歉。<br />\n<br />\n我們會密切監察2019新型冠狀病毒之情況，儘快將商品送至顧客手中，感謝各位顧客之理解。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港官網：<a href=\"https://www.nintendo.com.hk/support/information/2020/delay_02.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fsupport%2Finformation%2F2020%2Fdelay_02.html&d=%2FXNhycaKVB9NPWqbniWxn8kuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=388ad230\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nintendo.com.hk/support/information/2020/delay_02.html</a><br />\n<br />\n日本官網：<a href=\"https://www.nintendo.co.jp/support/information/2020/0206_01.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.co.jp%2Fsupport%2Finformation%2F2020%2F0206_01.html&d=%2FXNhycaKVB9NPWqbniWxn8kuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=6dbda965\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nintendo.co.jp/support/information/2020/0206_01.html</a>"},{"pid":"24475370b777b280d5f53dff42ff8ffdd9d0fdff","tid":1868330,"uid":79075,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T13:44:39.000Z","msg":"又貿易戰、又肺炎<br />\n到底啲外資肯撤廠未？？"},{"pid":"050adf8833fe2d745ba46d990268ea50df59d881","tid":1868330,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T13:46:11.000Z","msg":"兩盒🙏🏻非常感激"},{"pid":"94e704b508948d4edaec34680eeb8c56df418688","tid":1868330,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T14:42:44.000Z","msg":"翻譯:快D搶啦"}]}